column5: Just back from Canadian Tire Napanee.  Tickets for the May 5/6 tournament arrived today.  Also available at Dew Drop Inn, County Road 9 , Napanee, and Baker's Baits Napanee.  Staff informed us that the early bird price of $25, will be extended to Sunday April 22cd.  Good luck! Check it out here: http://quinte.com/walleye/registration.html bayboy and baygirl
You scared for a minute   I thought you meant they were sold out of the tickets already.  Looking forward to get the lines and boat wet again  Tundra
See your point.  Made the edit.  Also heard the tickets are at CTC, Kingston, Gardiners Road.  bayboy
I know they are avialable starting in Oshawa and points through Kingston...Will be getting our next week.
